Just because you don’t like a song does not mean it is trash. I’ve quite frankly had enough and I’m using my platform to speak on this. We gotta stop calling music trash that isn’t trash. Trash = untalented. Trash =no substance. Trash = poorly mixed. Trash = not catchy Trash = Overall Bad Record. Trash does not mean you don’t like a song or the artist behind it.

Positivity Post! I hope everybody has a wonderful and Merry Christmas this season filled with lots of presents, positivity and love. Spend time with friends and family and cherish those moments that we often take for granted. Surround yourself with people who inspire you to be the best version of yourself. Separate yourself from the negativity of the world and ensure your trees don’t bear bad fruit. Reach out to your friends and see if they’re ok. This is a tough time of year for a lot of people. I post this with love and wish all who read this in it’s entirety a Merry Merry Christmas 💯
